	[Amount] [money] NULL,

	[GrossAmount] [money] NULL,
	[ServiceStartDate] [datetime] NULL,
	[ServiceEndDate] [datetime] NULL,

(
	DISTRIBUTION = HASH ( [ClaimProcedureId] ),
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
